import React from 'react'
import { Box, CardFooter, Card, CardBody, Grid,I } from 'grommet'

function adminAccept() {
    return (
       <Box>
            <Grid gap="medium" rows="small" columns={{ count: 'fit', size: 'small' }}>
        
          <Card background='red' key='yo'>
            <CardBody pad="small">
              <Identifier
                pad="small"
                title='fs'
                subTitle='ff'
                size="small"
                align="start"
              >
                hi
              </Identifier>
            </CardBody>
            <CardFooter pad={{ horizontal: 'medium', vertical: 'small' }}>
              <Text size="xsmall">hell</Text>
            </CardFooter>
          </Card>
      
      </Grid>
       </Box>
    )
}

export default adminAccept
